### Business Logic
- Version increment: Automatic based on latest baseline
- Mileage projection: Monthly intervals using 30-day average or default 150 km/day
- Superseding: Previous baseline marked as SUPERSEDED with reference

### Dependencies
- AuditLog
- NotificationService
